---
export const prerender = true;

import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SectionDivider from '../../components/SectionDivider.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="All In For Sport — SuperBenefit"
  description="Testing web3-powered governance in community sport organizations."
>
  <section class="project-hero">
    <div class="project-hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="container project-hero-content">
      <span class="project-label">Experiment</span>
      <h1>All In For Sport</h1>
      <p class="project-subtitle">Testing web3-powered governance in community sport organizations</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <SectionDivider from="charcoal" to="cream" />

  <section class="project-content">
    <div class="container" data-animate="fade-up">
      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>What is AIFS?</h2>
        <p>
          All In For Sport (AIFS) applies the Reimagining Power framework to sport organizations, exploring how DAOs can empower athletes and communities.
        </p>
        <p>
          From an NFT funding project to a "coordi-nation" — AIFS documents how decentralized governance can work in practice.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>The Transformation</h2>
        <p>
          AIFS completed its transformation from an NFT-based funding project to a coordi-nation during its participation in the Reimagining Power Project from August 2024 to March 2025.
        </p>
        <p>
          The organization initially attempted to revolutionize grassroots sports funding through blockchain technology but evolved to become infrastructure that facilitates connections between Web3 innovation and community sports development.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>Challenges Addressed</h2>
        <ul class="challenge-list">
          <li>
            <strong>Value Proposition Confusion</strong> — Traditional philanthropists viewed Web3 elements as unnecessary complexity while crypto-native funders saw the shift away from NFTs as abandoning innovation
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Resource Constraints</strong> — Complete dependence on volunteer effort created unpredictable capacity and unfulfilled commitments
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Knowledge Gaps</strong> — Significant barriers between Web3 developers and grassroots sports organizations prevented meaningful collaboration
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>What They Did</h2>
        <p>Through RPP, AIFS implemented two parallel interventions:</p>
        
        <div class="interventions">
          <div class="intervention">
            <span class="intervention-num">01</span>
            <h4>The Gatherings Series</h4>
            <p>Brought together 111 participants across six sessions, creating structured spaces for cross-sector relationship building.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="intervention">
            <span class="intervention-num">02</span>
            <h4>Governance Transformation</h4>
            <p>Formalized through AIFSIP-04, establishing the organization's evolution into a coordi-nation model with autonomous cells within a networked structure.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>Outcomes</h2>
        <ul class="outcome-list">
          <li>Clarified identity as coordination infrastructure</li>
          <li>Developed governance structures enabling partnerships with organizations like Women Win</li>
          <li>Selected for the IOC Tech365 initiative supporting 25 organizations across 16 countries</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="content-block">
        <h2>Resources</h2>
        <div class="resource-links">
          <a href="https://knowledge.superbenefit.org/artifacts/reimagining-power/aifs-experiment-case-study" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="resource-link">
            <span class="resource-icon">📖</span>
            <span class="resource-title">Case Study</span>
            <span class="resource-desc">Full transformation documentation</span>
          </a>
          <a href="https://knowledge.superbenefit.org/artifacts/reimagining-power/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="resource-link">
            <span class="resource-icon">🌱</span>
            <span class="resource-title">RPP Knowledge Base</span>
            <span class="resource-desc">More about the broader project</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <SectionDivider from="cream" to="charcoal" />

  <section class="project-cta">
    <div class="container" data-animate="fade-up">
      <h2>Want to learn more or get involved?</h2>
      <p>Reach out on Discord or explore the knowledge base.</p>
      <div class="cta-links">
        <a href="https://discord.gg/d2EeszTvVm" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="cta-btn">Join Discord</a>
        <a href="https://knowledge.superbenefit.org/artifacts/reimagining-power/aifs-experiment-case-study" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="cta-btn cta-btn--secondary">Explore AIFS</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .project-hero {
    position: relative;
    background: var(--color-charcoal);
    background-image: url('/images/brand-showcase.webp');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    padding-block-start: calc(var(--header-height) + var(--space-2xl));
    padding-block-end: var(--space-2xl);
    min-height: 50vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
  }

  .project-hero-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(
      to bottom,
      rgba(76, 175, 80, 0.6) 0%,
      rgba(56, 139, 115, 0.7) 50%,
      rgba(45, 45, 45, 0.95) 100%
    );
  }

  .project-hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .project-label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--color-green-light);
    margin-block-end: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .project-hero h1 {
    color: var(--color-cream);
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    margin-block-end: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .project-subtitle {
    color: var(--color-cream);
    opacity: 0.9;
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .project-content {
    background: var(--color-cream);
    padding-block: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .project-content .container {
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .content-block {
    margin-block-end: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .content-block h2 {
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    margin-block-end: var(--space-md);
  }

  .content-block p {
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    opacity: 0.85;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-block-end: var(--space-md);
  }

  .challenge-list,
  .outcome-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .challenge-list li,
  .outcome-list li {
    padding: var(--space-md);
    background: var(--color-cream-light);
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-block-end: var(--space-sm);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-green-sage);
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    opacity: 0.85;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .challenge-list li strong {
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
  }

  .outcome-list li::before {
    content: "✓ ";
    color: var(--color-green-sage);
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .interventions {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    margin-block-start: var(--space-lg);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .interventions {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .intervention {
    background: var(--color-cream-light);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  .intervention-num {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--color-green-sage);
    opacity: 0.4;
    margin-block-end: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .intervention h4 {
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    margin-block-end: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .intervention p {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    opacity: 0.75;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .resource-links {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .resource-links {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  .resource-link {
    display: block;
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    background: var(--color-cream-light);
    border-radius: 12px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: transform var(--transition-fast), box-shadow var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .resource-link:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
  }

  .resource-icon {
    display: block;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin-block-end: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .resource-title {
    display: block;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    margin-block-end: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .resource-desc {
    display: block;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  .project-cta {
    background: var(--color-charcoal);
    padding-block: var(--space-2xl);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .project-cta h2 {
    color: var(--color-cream);
    margin-block-end: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .project-cta p {
    color: var(--color-cream);
    opacity: 0.8;
    margin-block-end: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .cta-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .cta-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.8em 1.8em;
    background: var(--color-green-sage);
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
    font-weight: 600;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: transform var(--transition-fast), background var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .cta-btn:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    background: var(--color-green-light);
  }

  .cta-btn--secondary {
    background: transparent;
    border: 2px solid var(--color-cream);
    color: var(--color-cream);
  }

  .cta-btn--secondary:hover {
    background: var(--color-cream);
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
  }
</style>
